\c 14
\s Jehovha anodana Israeri kuti adzokere kwaari
\p
\v 1 Dzoka, Israeri, kuna Jehovha Mwari wako; nokuti wakagumburwa nechitadzo chako.
\v 2 Torai mashoko \add awa\add* pamwe nemwi, mugodzokera kuna Jehovha, muti kwaari: Bvisa uipi hwose mugo\add ti\add*gamuchira nenyasha, naizvozvo ticharipa hando dzemiromo yedu.
\v 3 Asiriya havangatiponesi; haangatasvi mabhiza; uye hatichazotizve kubasa remaoko edu: \add Muri\add* vamwari vedu; nokuti mamuri nherera inowana nyasha.
\p
\v 4 Ndichaporesa kudzokera shure kwavo, ndichavada pachena; nokuti kutsamwa kwangu kwadzoka kubva kwaari.
\v 5 Ndichava sedova kuna Israeri; achatunga seruva, uye achatanda midzi yake seRebhanoni.
\v 6 Matavi ake achakura, uye kubwinya kwake kuchava semuti wemuorivhi, nemunhuhwi wake seRebhanoni.
\v 7 Vanogara mumumvuri wake vachadzoka; vachavandudzika \add se\add*zviyo, nekutunga semuzambiringa; chirangaridzo chake \add chichaita\add* sewaini yeRebhanoni.
\v 8 Efuremu, ndichinei nezvifananidzo? Ini ndaka\add mu\add*pindura, ndakamucherekedza; ndikava semuti wemufiri munyoro; chibereko chako chinowanikwa kubva kwandiri.
\p
\v 9 Ndiani wakachenjera? Zvino achanzwisisa izvi. Wakangwara? Zvino achazviziva. Nokuti nzira dzaJehovha dzakarurama; uye vakarurama vachafamba madziri; asi vadariki vachagumburwa madziri.